reviewText: This is a great PPV!  The DVD came in great shape, and was still packaged.  A lot of finishes and a joy to watch/have in the collection.

Not going to say too much about this because everyone has their own opinions about these UFC events but, with the women getting involved now the newer events have been going up in star ratings for me. Here is the lineup for this particular event:

Matt The Immoratal Brown vs Ryan The Tank Engine Thomas
Alvin Kid Robinson vs Mark Bocek
Jeremy Lil' Heathen Stephens vs Rafael dos Anjos
Jorge JG Gurgel vs Aaron Riley
Tamdan The Barn Cat McCrory vs Dustin Hazelett
Nate Rock Quarry vs Demian Maia
Gabriel Napao Gonzaga vs Josh Heavy Hendricks
Joe Daddy Stevenson vs Kenny KenFlo Florian
Main Event: Brock Lesnar vs Randy The Natural Couture
